Gramática

    0 $accept: StFile $end

    1 StFile: Blocks System
    2       | Blocks
    3       | System

    4 Blocks: Blocks FunctionBlock
    5       | FunctionBlock
    6       | CustomFunctionBlock

    7 $@1: %empty

    8 $@2: %empty

    9 $@3: %empty

   10 $@4: %empty

   11 $@5: %empty

   12 $@6: %empty

